title: Fever,Cough and Body Pain
description: The treatment for fever, cough, and body pain will depend on the underlying cause of these symptoms.

title: Fracture Treatment
description: The treatment for a fracture (a broken bone) will depend on the type, location, and severity of the fracture. In general, the goals of treatment are to reduce pain, promote healing, and prevent complications.
